We've got options for

00:00:27.003 --> 00:00:29.780
making sure that they all fit within this column on the right.

00:00:29.780 --> 00:00:33.435
Either, we could go into each class here and style its HTML and

00:00:33.435 --> 00:00:38.670
CSS individually to make sure that they all fit on the right side of the screen.

